  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The title of this article is conjecture and may be subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Siege of Seagard</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Seagard\" title=\"Seagard\">Seagard</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">Frey</a> victory</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/33px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png\" width=\"33\" height=\"36\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/50px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/66px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a></b>/ <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing\">House Baratheon of King's Landing</a>:<br />\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Frey.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/30px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/45px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/60px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Stark.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/30px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/45px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/60px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">Kingdom of the North</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">the Trident</a></b>/ <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a>:<br />\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Tully.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Tully.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/30px-House_Tully.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/45px-House_Tully.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/60px-House_Tully.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">House Tully</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Mallister\" title=\"House Mallister\">House Mallister</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Frey.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/20px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/30px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/40px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey_(son_of_Ryman)\" title=\"Walder Frey (son of Ryman)\">\"Black\" Walder Frey</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Mallister.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Mallister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/75/House_Mallister.svg/20px-House_Mallister.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/75/House_Mallister.svg/30px-House_Mallister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/75/House_Mallister.svg/40px-House_Mallister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Mallister\" title=\"Jason Mallister\">Jason Mallister</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Mallister\" title=\"Jason Mallister\">Jason Mallister</a> (POW)<br />Unknown total</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>siege of Seagard</b> occurs late in the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Siege\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Siege</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Siege_of_Seagard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Prior to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a>'s marriage to <a href=\"/index.php/Roslin_Frey\" title=\"Roslin Frey\">Roslin Frey</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">King of the Trident</a>, sends Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Mallister\" title=\"Jason Mallister\">Jason Mallister</a> back to his seat of <a href=\"/index.php/Seagard\" title=\"Seagard\">Seagard</a>. Jason is tasked with using <a href=\"/index.php/House_Mallister\" title=\"House Mallister\">Mallister</a> longships to take <a href=\"/index.php/Galbart_Glover\" title=\"Galbart Glover\">Galbart Glover</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Maege_Mormont\" title=\"Maege Mormont\">Maege Mormont</a> into the <a href=\"/index.php/Neck\" title=\"Neck\">Neck</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a> betrays Robb in the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Wedding\" title=\"Red Wedding\">Red Wedding</a>, however, and Jason's son, <a href=\"/index.php/Patrek_Mallister\" title=\"Patrek Mallister\">Patrek</a>, is taken captive at the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Siege\">Siege</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Siege_of_Seagard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Siege\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>While the Freys are now supporters of King <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey I Baratheon</a>, the Mallisters remain loyal to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey_(son_of_Ryman)\" title=\"Walder Frey (son of Ryman)\">\"Black\" Walder Frey</a> commands a Frey siege of Seagard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Although Jason resists at first, he yields the castle when Black Walder threatens to hang Patrek before the walls of Seagard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Siege_of_Seagard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>House Mallister submits to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> but Lord Jason and Patrek are held captive by the Freys within Seagard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Siege_of_Seagard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_45\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 45\">Chapter 45</a>, Catelyn V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_53\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 53\">Chapter 53</a>, Tyrion VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_38\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 38\">Chapter 38</a>, Jaime VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_33\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 33\">Chapter 33</a>, Jaime V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autoco